-- Baseball Union Head Weiner Is Being Treated for Brain Tumor
-- B y   C u r t i s   E i c h e l b e r g e r
-- 2012-08-21T18:52:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-21/baseball-union-head-weiner-is-being-treated-for-brain-tumor.html
Michael Weiner , the head of the
Major League Baseball Players Association, is being treated for
a brain tumor, the union said in a statement.  Weiner, 50, began what is expected to be a month of
treatment yesterday and will work out of the union’s New York
office on a daily basis, according to the statement. It didn’t
give any details on the illness.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  